                        <interp inst="t18540403-name-386" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS WALLMAN</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City policeman</hi>, 400). Mr. Holloway gave the prisoner into my custody—he was holding him by the collar, and had this handkerchief (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>) in his hand—I searched the prisoner, and found on him two pocket handkerchiefs, one silk and the other cambric, a tobacco box and a knife (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>).</p>
